43
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:01,170
It&#39;s not good enough just to hear it.

44
00:03:01,170 --> 00:03:06,170
You have to be in a social context where people are communicating, and you can have a rich

45
00:03:06,170 --> 00:03:09,099
sense of what they&#39;re talking about.

46
00:03:09,099 --> 00:03:12,032
It takes that in order for babies to learn language (Baldwin, 1994; Ramirez-Esparza,

47
